Map
The
MIT Campus Map
provides a searchable, graphic view of MIT. Questions, corrections, and suggestions should be directed to
campus-map@mit.edu
.
Accessibility
MIT is committed to providing an environment that is
accessible
to individuals with disabilities. If you cannot access content or use features on our website due to a disability, please
let us know
.
